  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "STOREMAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><p>*Organize and assist in day-to-day operation of store.</p></p><p><p>*Prepare incoming and outgoing inspection.</p></p><p><p>*Issue and inspect all goods for compliance to the deliver order.</p></p><p><p>*Picking & Packing of goods.</p></p><p><p>*Perform loading/unloading/arranging of warehouse cargo and items.</p></p><p><p>*Manage inventory accuracy though monitoring of daily store activities.</p></p><p><p>*Assist to perform cycle count and stock take when needed.</p></p><p><p>*Perform stock data entry transaction in the inventory system.</p></p><p><p>*To comply with security and safety rules and regulations.</p></p><p><p>*Maintain good housekeeping in the warehouse and store area.</p></p><p><p>*To carry out and perform refilling duties and prepare refilling records.</p></p><p>*Perform any other duties as assigned by immediate superior most optimal route.</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants may apply for interview.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
